{"tid":2156580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[開定] [蓁眉李貌] 2020年高雄市市長補選，即時開票討論區","createTime":"2020-08-14T13:59:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T09:31:41.000Z","uid":52658,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"cc0c47c2a7b4f2ab330c3d63e57c2d2ec923b4a5","tid":2156580,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T13:59:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s9ZVUPQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs9ZVUPQ.png&h=cc6597b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日係選前之夜 韓國瑜再度現身高雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n條帶賽仔一開口講野就落大雨😪<br />\n<br />\n講下先 呢場係罷韓後既高雄市長補選<br />\n<br />\n1. 陳其邁 民進黨<br />\n2. 吳益政 民眾黨/親民黨<br />\n3. 李眉蓁 國民黨<br />\n<br />\n其實都無咩好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />54088躺贏<br />\n<br />\n陳其邁係超挺香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MOy7L1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMOy7L1f.jpg&h=2afa0895&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/HatePolitics/M.1597409341.A.36A.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FHatePolitics%2FM.1597409341.A.36A.html&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcbhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=658dd23e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/HatePolitics/M.1597409341.A.36A.html</a><br />\n<br />\n暫時未有開票既link <br />\n有會放上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日大約4點 投票會結束<br />\n6點到7點左右就會有結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"230984bec23c59e38abb19511f2811a4b2d8d1af","tid":2156580,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T14:01:30.000Z","msg":"中國國民黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f69d21ef2a229e4753ae431e1863b644e7e11f","tid":2156